import { Card, CardTypography } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

function Message(props) {
  return (
    <Card>
      <CardContent>
        <Typography
          color="white"
          variant="h5"
          component="h2"
        >
          {props.username} : {props.text}
        </Typography>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default Message
